1
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 10=
(Identity Crisis)

3
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:24,680
He Jinchen

4
00:01:25,159 --> 00:01:26,760
is the one behind Meiyan International.

5
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:31,120
He sent all these people here.

6
00:01:31,519 --> 00:01:32,000
Also,

7
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:33,760
your car accidents

8
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:36,000
were probably his doing to stop you

9
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:37,480
from investigating Meiyan International.

10
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,480
The He family is too dangerous.

11
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:42,200
It's good that you are not going back.

12
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,359
No.

13
00:01:44,719 --> 00:01:45,480
I have to go back.

14
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:46,239
Why?

15
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:49,560
Because I now suspect my mother's death

16
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,920
is related to TAF990.

17
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:55,200
My mother was also a journalist.

18
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:56,799
Eight years ago,

19
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:58,719
she received a phone call that night.

20
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:06,599
(Hello?)

21
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:08,919
(Alright, I got it.)

22
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:09,960
(I will go right now.)

23
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,199
(Mom.)

24
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,199
(You are injured,)

25
00:02:15,319 --> 00:02:16,479
(and you even received
a threatening letter.)

26
00:02:17,159 --> 00:02:19,280
(Are you really going to
keep digging into this story?)

27
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,319
(It is my duty)

28
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,039
(to never let the truth be buried.)

29
00:02:26,199 --> 00:02:28,000
(Let's go, let me take you there.)

30
00:02:29,639 --> 00:02:30,680
(Stay home and lock the door.)

31
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,759
(Mom, be careful.)

32
00:02:44,900 --> 00:02:46,500
(Cosmetic Raw Material Investigation)

33
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:47,700
(Ingredient: TAF990?)

34
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,159
Then after she left with my father,

35
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,280
they never came back.

36
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:53,960
A phone call?

37
00:02:56,479 --> 00:02:57,199
Was it

38
00:02:58,479 --> 00:02:59,199
my father

39
00:02:59,919 --> 00:03:01,400
who tipped off your mother?

40
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,319
They all died on the same day.

41
00:03:05,599 --> 00:03:07,439
Your father was also connected
to Meiyan International?

42
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,719
My father was once a shareholder

43
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,599
of Meiyan International.

44
00:03:11,479 --> 00:03:12,080
Eight years ago,

45
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:13,919
he died in the fire

46
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,360
at the cosmetics factory

47
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,639
for no reason.

48
00:03:19,639 --> 00:03:20,360
I suspect

49
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,759
he found issues with the raw materials,

50
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:24,240
so He Jinchen killed him.

51
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:28,879
He Jinchen is really ruthless!

52
00:03:31,479 --> 00:03:32,520
At the scene of your car accident,

53
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,840
I found a USB drive.

54
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,159
The data in this USB drive

55
00:03:37,879 --> 00:03:39,599
also mentioned TAF990.

56
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,680
The USB drive is with you?

57
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,280
I thought I had lost it.

58
00:03:44,319 --> 00:03:45,439
I have checked the data inside.

59
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:46,879
It is true that

60
00:03:48,199 --> 00:03:50,319
Tian Gang made up most of it.

61
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,039
But

62
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:53,759
he mentioned TAF990.

63
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:57,800
We can follow that lead and dig deeper.

64
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:58,840
Perhaps

65
00:03:59,479 --> 00:04:01,159
we can find leverage against He Jinchen.

66
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:02,719
I'll find you a place to stay

67
00:04:03,479 --> 00:04:04,439
in the next few days.

68
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:05,520
You should lay low for a while.

69
00:04:05,719 --> 00:04:06,120
No.

70
00:04:06,599 --> 00:04:07,400
I am going back to the He family.

71
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,439
It's too dangerous there.

72
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:11,280
If you go back, I will be worried.

73
00:04:11,759 --> 00:04:13,599
I don't want to see them either.

74
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:14,439
But

75
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:16,480
if I go in as Gu Qingmei,

76
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:18,199
I might be able to find out more.

77
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,560
At least I can use Gu Corporation

78
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,600
to fight back against them.

79
00:04:25,759 --> 00:04:26,199
Alright.

80
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,519
Since you have made up your mind,

81
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,240
then let's join forces.

82
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,199
Alright.

83
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,279
My partner.

84
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:33,360
My...

85
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:35,920
My partner!

86
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,120
Qingmei,

87
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:49,600
about what happened before,

88
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,439
I apologize to you on their behalf.

89
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,199
Don't take it to heart.

90
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:55,839
It is alright, Dad.

91
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:57,439
I did not take it to heart.

92
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,279
Qingmei,

93
00:05:01,079 --> 00:05:03,639
This tonic soup is specially for you.

94
00:05:04,199 --> 00:05:05,160
It'll help you recover.

95
00:05:07,439 --> 00:05:10,399
You seem to be getting along.

96
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,560
Being a daughter-in-law of the He family

97
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,319
is not that easy.

98
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:20,839
You're right.

99
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:24,240
Being a son of the He family
is not that easy either.

100
00:05:24,879 --> 00:05:26,800
I heard recently Jinchuan

101
00:05:27,319 --> 00:05:28,319
has been making big money.

102
00:05:30,399 --> 00:05:31,480
Not that big of a project.

103
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:33,199
Just testing the waters
with some friends.

104
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,639
Didn't you tell me
it's already turning a profit?

105
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,160
Jinchuan,

106
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,199
the investment climate
is less than ideal right now.

107
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,639
You should be cautious.

108
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:41,680
Jinchen,

109
00:05:42,199 --> 00:05:42,800
you don't understand.

110
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,759
My project is reliable,

111
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,600
and the profit margins are very high.

112
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:47,839
That's right.

113
00:05:47,959 --> 00:05:49,120
I even invested twenty million.

114
00:05:49,439 --> 00:05:50,560
That impressive?

115
00:05:50,879 --> 00:05:51,639
Have you gotten your dividends yet?

116
00:05:52,519 --> 00:05:53,839
If you get dividends,

117
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,720
don't forget about us.

118
00:05:56,639 --> 00:05:57,279
Dear,

119
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,959
when are you going to
give me my dividends?

120
00:05:59,279 --> 00:06:00,279
Soon.

121
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:01,199
Very soon.

122
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:02,000
Let's have dinner.

123
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,399
Second Young Master,

124
00:06:06,639 --> 00:06:07,399
there is a document for you.

125
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,680
Some people

126
00:06:13,639 --> 00:06:16,639
just won't learn
until they hit rock bottom.

127
00:06:19,519 --> 00:06:20,120
Everyone,

128
00:06:21,639 --> 00:06:23,600
this is a paternity test report.

129
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,720
Today, I am going to prove to everyone

130
00:06:26,519 --> 00:06:27,800
that this woman

131
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:30,160
is not Gu Qingmei!

132
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:35,480
All the Gu family members are gone.

133
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,079
Who are you going to test me against?

134
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,279
Bet you didn't know.

135
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:42,600
The bone marrow of Gu Qingmei's father
is still stored at the hospital.

136
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,439
A DNA test is more than enough.

137
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,319
So,

138
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:49,480
who are you, imposter?

139
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,600
Why are you faking Gu Qingmei?

140
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,519
(Mu Shaoze)
Report, safe.

141
00:07:01,140 --> 00:07:01,980
(DNA Testing Center)

142
00:07:03,319 --> 00:07:04,120
Why wouldn't you let me see it?

143
00:07:04,879 --> 00:07:07,519
Could it be a forged report?

144
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,160
Of course it is real!

145
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:12,199
You imposter,

146
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:14,160
get out of my family right now!

147
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:16,319
Otherwise, I will not go easy on you!

148
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:20,439
I told you to cut down on the drinking!

149
00:07:20,839 --> 00:07:21,680
Stop making a scene here!

150
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,000
Your sister-in-law just came back.

151
00:07:23,199 --> 00:07:24,240
What nonsense are you talking about now?

152
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:25,839
See for yourself!

153
00:07:29,380 --> 00:07:31,020
(Gu Qingmei's biological father)

154
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,079
Impossible!

155
00:07:34,399 --> 00:07:35,639
How could she be the real daughter?

156
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,959
She can't be Gu Qingmei!

157
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:38,120
Enough!

158
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:40,879
You are absolutely ridiculous.

159
00:07:41,319 --> 00:07:43,800
Can't we just have a quiet family meal?

160
00:07:44,319 --> 00:07:45,759
If you can't behave, get out!

161
00:07:46,519 --> 00:07:47,319
Forget it, forget it.

162
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,720
He must have just lost his head
for a moment.

163
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:50,480
Come on.

164
00:08:02,319 --> 00:08:04,079
I asked Assistant Tang
and found out you are here.

165
00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:05,839
I did not know
you were this good at golf.

166
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,079
When I'm in a bad mood,

167
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:10,759
a few swings really do help.

168
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:16,240
Thank you for the paternity test.

169
00:08:16,519 --> 00:08:17,439
If it weren't for your help,

170
00:08:17,839 --> 00:08:19,040
I might have been exposed by now.

171
00:08:20,439 --> 00:08:21,519
Actually,

172
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,160
I did not do much.

173
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:25,839
That test report was real all along.

174
00:08:28,199 --> 00:08:30,079
You're not your parents'
biological daughter, are you?

175
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,159
I was actually adopted.

176
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,759
I could never figure out

177
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:38,320
why my biological parents abandoned me.

178
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:42,279
I have already sent people
to look for Gu Qingmei.

179
00:08:42,879 --> 00:08:43,600
Once we find her,

180
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:46,200
I believe everything will come to light.

181
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:50,879
Give it a try.

182
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:53,279
Why not?

183
00:08:53,799 --> 00:08:55,039
I pick things up quickly.

184
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:57,879
Perfect.

185
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,000
Mr. Mu will teach you.

186
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,399
Left hand on top.

187
00:09:03,879 --> 00:09:05,840
Then feet shoulder-width apart.

188
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:08,600
Then

189
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:10,600
lift.

190
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,360
Straighten your left arm.

191
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:15,960
I'll leave it to you.

192
00:09:23,879 --> 00:09:24,440
How is it?

193
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,679
A good teacher produces great students.

194
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,159
Let's talk business.

195
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:32,559
How is the investigation
into Meiyan International going?

196
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:35,919
Every part of Meiyan's operation
is locked down tight.

197
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:36,960
It is very hard to dig deeper.

198
00:09:37,679 --> 00:09:39,919
Unless we get into
the core operations of Meiyan

199
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,639
and find a breakthrough from the inside.

200
00:09:42,399 --> 00:09:43,399
A breakthrough...

201
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,440
I've got an idea.

202
00:09:47,980 --> 00:09:50,020
(Gu Corporation)

203
00:09:51,559 --> 00:09:52,600
Mr. Zhang, this way please.

204
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:53,759
Madam Gu is waiting for you inside.

205
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:54,559
Thank you.

206
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:01,759
Hello, Madam Gu.

207
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:06,960
Mr. Zhang, you're here.

208
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,279
Su Li, you...

209
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,240
Call me Madam Gu here.

210
00:10:13,879 --> 00:10:14,799
What is going on?

211
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:15,639
For the past month, you...

212
00:10:18,879 --> 00:10:20,159
I thought something had happened to you.

213
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,679
If the editor had not stopped me
that day,

214
00:10:21,799 --> 00:10:22,879
I would have called the police.

215
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,679
So much has happened

216
00:10:24,879 --> 00:10:26,360
these days.

217
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:28,120
It's enough to fill
a whole feature article.

218
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:34,440
Boss.

219
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:37,519
Boss.

220
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:39,720
Boss.

221
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:41,080
Speak.

222
00:10:41,679 --> 00:10:42,919
Tian Gang has suddenly disappeared.

223
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:44,840
Why?

224
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:45,840
I don't know either.

225
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:47,720
I just went to the bathroom

226
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:48,840
and he was gone.

227
00:10:49,519 --> 00:10:50,200
Go find him now!

228
00:10:50,799 --> 00:10:52,679
He must not fall into
He Jinchen's hands!

229
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:53,440
Yes!

230
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:03,840
Su Li,

231
00:11:04,399 --> 00:11:06,320
you really go all out for an exclusive.

232
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:08,919
The exclusive is not what matters.

233
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:10,399
What matters

234
00:11:10,559 --> 00:11:11,559
is getting to the truth.

235
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:12,600
Oh, by the way...

236
00:11:12,799 --> 00:11:13,320
Chao,

237
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,600
don't tell anyone

238
00:11:15,159 --> 00:11:16,399
about us being in touch.

239
00:11:16,919 --> 00:11:18,000
Don't worry, Su Li.

240
00:11:19,159 --> 00:11:20,399
Is there anything I can help with?

241
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,159
I want to expose

242
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:24,120
the Meiyan International scandal
I have been investigating.

243
00:11:24,279 --> 00:11:26,159
The editor's holding back the files.

244
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,080
He said there is not enough evidence.

245
00:11:28,279 --> 00:11:29,799
Luckily, I made a backup beforehand.

246
00:11:30,679 --> 00:11:31,320
But

247
00:11:31,559 --> 00:11:33,639
we cannot officially publish it
right now.

248
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:35,840
That is fine.

249
00:11:36,879 --> 00:11:38,440
If the formal channels are blocked,

250
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,559
then we will play by their rules.

251
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,720
We will find a way eventually.

252
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,720
Even if you are a daughter
of the Gu family,

253
00:11:59,159 --> 00:12:00,759
you are definitely not Gu Qingmei.

254
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:02,679
You can fool others,

255
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,519
but you cannot fool me.

256
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,440
What else are you planning to
threaten me with?

257
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,080
Don't get too cocky.

258
00:12:08,519 --> 00:12:10,440
I will definitely kick you out of here!

259
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:11,919
Sure.

260
00:12:12,159 --> 00:12:13,559
I might as well tell them

261
00:12:13,759 --> 00:12:15,440
how you threatened Gu Qingmei

262
00:12:15,639 --> 00:12:16,480
into selling her jewelry
to fund your investment.

263
00:12:17,679 --> 00:12:19,679
You think that's enough to hold over me?

264
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,399
We will see.

265
00:12:28,679 --> 00:12:30,279
(I won't let you ruin my plan.)

266
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:31,840
(He Jinchuan,)

267
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,960
(you brought this upon yourself.)

268
00:12:56,220 --> 00:13:00,980
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

269
00:13:00,980 --> 00:13:05,820
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

270
00:13:05,820 --> 00:13:10,380
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

271
00:13:10,380 --> 00:13:15,300
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

272
00:13:15,300 --> 00:13:19,100
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

273
00:13:19,100 --> 00:13:23,900
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

274
00:13:23,900 --> 00:13:26,740
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

275
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:29,420
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

276
00:13:29,780 --> 00:13:35,340
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

277
00:13:35,740 --> 00:13:42,540
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

278
00:13:42,820 --> 00:13:47,500
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

279
00:13:47,660 --> 00:13:54,460
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

280
00:13:54,780 --> 00:14:01,580
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

281
00:14:01,780 --> 00:14:06,260
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

282
00:14:06,260 --> 00:14:09,620
